≡ 
<taxonomicName family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="D." higherTaxonomySource="treatment-meta" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="D. caryophyllus subsp. sylvestris" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" rank="subSpecies" species="caryophyllus" subSpecies="sylvestris">D. caryophyllus subsp. sylvestris</taxonomicName>
(Wulfen) Rouy &amp; Foucaud, Fl. France 3: 193. 1896. Ind. Loc.: - &quot;in montibus illis prope Ponewitsch Baronis Wolkensberg in Carniolia, tum in M. Utocsek prope Pillichgraz; in iis. Vallis Rablensis; denique &amp; in iis Vallis Canalensis &amp;c.&quot;.
</paragraph>
